WEBVTT

00:19.880 --> 00:22.120
This is the cold entering the body.

00:22.640 --> 00:25.320
She's reached a life-threatening pass now.

00:26.720 --> 00:28.760
We need to scrape her
and activate the blood circulation,

00:29.280 --> 00:30.880
unblock the meridians.

00:31.920 --> 00:34.960
Is there a woman here

00:35.480 --> 00:36.840
who can help with the scraping?

00:37.960 --> 00:39.320
I'm her husband.

00:39.840 --> 00:40.840
I can do it.

00:46.880 --> 00:48.680
Wrap her tight in the blankets.

00:49.200 --> 00:51.560
Remove her outer clothing.

04:49.920 --> 04:54.640
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

05:14.480 --> 05:15.520
Father…

05:17.920 --> 05:18.800
Mother…

05:22.840 --> 05:27.120
Father! Mother! Where are you?

05:33.760 --> 05:34.600
Father.

05:35.720 --> 05:36.800
Mother.

05:38.960 --> 05:39.880
Father.

05:40.480 --> 05:41.480
Mother.

05:42.000 --> 05:43.480
Wait for me.

05:46.600 --> 05:47.440
No…

05:47.520 --> 05:49.440
Changyu, be good. Go back.

05:49.520 --> 05:50.560
Go back now.

05:51.080 --> 05:52.240
Where are you going?

05:52.760 --> 05:55.720
Changyu, look after your sister.

05:55.800 --> 05:56.840
And yourself.

05:57.640 --> 05:58.480
No…

05:58.560 --> 06:00.200
Take me with you, Mother.

06:01.280 --> 06:02.120
We're leaving.

06:02.640 --> 06:05.160
If you're leaving, take me too.

06:06.480 --> 06:07.920
Father.

06:10.080 --> 06:11.520
Mother.

06:18.240 --> 06:20.040
Father.

06:22.640 --> 06:23.840
Father.

06:23.920 --> 06:24.800
Mother.

06:27.080 --> 06:28.120
A nightmare?

06:30.720 --> 06:32.000
It's alright.

06:32.800 --> 06:33.680
I'm here.

06:36.000 --> 06:37.040
Don't leave me.

06:39.760 --> 06:42.400
I've killed enough men
to carry heavy karma.

06:44.200 --> 06:45.720
With me beside you,

06:46.320 --> 06:47.720
no spirits would dare come near.

07:00.080 --> 07:01.200
Wu.

07:01.920 --> 07:03.720
Back where you're from,

07:03.800 --> 07:05.640
that calls for marriage, doesn't it?

07:07.160 --> 07:08.240
I swore to stay quiet.

07:08.320 --> 07:09.480
Don't drag me into it.

07:09.560 --> 07:10.800
Come on.

07:10.880 --> 07:11.920
Just say it.

07:12.000 --> 07:13.760
After all that,
of course he'd have to marry--

07:14.520 --> 07:16.120
-Marquis.
-Marquis.

07:19.680 --> 07:20.520
Hand it over.

07:24.680 --> 07:25.800
Marquis…

08:36.120 --> 08:37.000
Changyu.

08:40.120 --> 08:43.039
Will you let me take you as my wife?

08:46.600 --> 08:48.320
If you stay silent,

08:49.280 --> 08:51.080
I'll take it as a yes.

09:02.800 --> 09:04.800
Where is the Marquis? I bring urgent news.

09:05.840 --> 09:07.160
He may still be resting.

09:07.240 --> 09:09.720
-He stayed by that woman all night.
-All night?

09:10.920 --> 09:11.760
What is she to him?

09:12.640 --> 09:13.520
Don't ask me.

09:13.600 --> 09:15.000
If you're so curious, ask him yourself.

09:20.320 --> 09:21.320
What is it?

09:21.400 --> 09:22.240
Marquis.

09:22.840 --> 09:23.920
Marquis.

09:24.000 --> 09:25.600
We've found
Qingfeng Stronghold's remnants.

09:25.680 --> 09:26.960
They're hiding in the rear hills.

09:27.680 --> 09:29.720
The bandit we questioned confessed

09:29.800 --> 09:31.880
they were bribed by Sui Yuanqing.

09:32.880 --> 09:35.680
He also said
on the night Lin'an was massacred,

09:35.760 --> 09:37.920
Sui Yuanqing tried to force himself
on that woman.

09:39.680 --> 09:40.920
It seems…

09:41.920 --> 09:42.760
she was the target.

09:45.760 --> 09:48.360
Ready the horses.
Xie Wu and Xie Qi stay here.

09:48.880 --> 09:50.880
The rest of the Blood-clad,
move out with me. Quietly.

09:55.520 --> 09:57.560
NORTHWEST POST STATION

09:57.640 --> 09:59.080
Respectful report to Chancellor Wei.

09:59.600 --> 10:01.440
I have reached the Yanzhou camp

10:01.520 --> 10:02.760
and met with Marquis Wu'an.

10:03.800 --> 10:06.080
Though he harbors doubts
about the Jinzhou matter,

10:06.600 --> 10:08.440
he lacks solid proof.

10:08.520 --> 10:09.880
You may rest assured.

10:10.640 --> 10:12.440
His stance towards you remains uncertain.

10:12.520 --> 10:15.000
I will keep on watching
and report without delay.

10:16.000 --> 10:16.840
Sheng.

10:19.120 --> 10:19.960
Come in.

10:24.440 --> 10:25.320
Sheng.

10:25.400 --> 10:26.440
Marquis Wu'an has gone to Lin'an.

10:26.520 --> 10:27.880
He wiped out Qingfeng Stronghold.

10:28.560 --> 10:31.040
That wretched little den
was worth his trouble?

10:31.120 --> 10:33.720
Qingfeng's bandits were instigated
by Sui Yuanqing.

10:33.800 --> 10:34.640
They massacred Lin'an.

10:36.280 --> 10:37.960
That little town of Lin'an…

10:40.200 --> 10:41.760
By the Chancellor's estimation,

10:42.440 --> 10:45.440
Prince Changxin's next move
should be Lucheng.

10:46.280 --> 10:49.560
Sui Yuanqing is his favorite son.

10:49.640 --> 10:51.680
At such a crucial moment,

10:52.200 --> 10:55.240
why abandon Lucheng
to slaughter a minor town?

10:56.680 --> 10:57.920
I cannot say.

10:58.440 --> 11:00.120
But there is something else.

11:00.200 --> 11:02.680
The Marquis entered an uxorilocal marriage

11:03.440 --> 11:04.680
while recovering in Lin'an.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.840
What?

11:20.200 --> 11:22.080
Shisan Niang--

11:23.400 --> 11:24.920
My brother is dead.

11:25.760 --> 11:27.480
You led him to slaughter Lin'an.

11:27.560 --> 11:29.960
Why didn't you bring him back alive?

11:50.800 --> 11:52.080
Marquis Wu'an issued a kill order.

11:52.160 --> 11:54.280
Qingfeng Stronghold was to be erased.

11:54.800 --> 11:57.560
Anyone captured was gutted
and left hanging for three days.

11:58.200 --> 12:00.080
He sent a hundred Blood-clad cavalry.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.400
Do you know what that means?

12:03.360 --> 12:05.560
They could raze your stronghold
a hundred times over.

12:06.360 --> 12:09.200
The fact you're standing here unharmed

12:09.880 --> 12:12.120
is already mercy from heaven.

12:17.760 --> 12:18.920
Mercy?

12:20.680 --> 12:23.080
Am I meant to thank him for it?

12:31.840 --> 12:33.000
Listen carefully.

12:33.520 --> 12:36.360
It was a woman named Fan Changyu
who killed your brother.

12:37.640 --> 12:39.080
If you want revenge, go find her.

12:39.600 --> 12:40.680
Do not trouble me again.

12:41.200 --> 12:43.120
I will flay her alive.

12:50.720 --> 12:51.840
Wait.

12:56.240 --> 12:57.520
Who is the child?

12:59.080 --> 13:00.280
Isn't it obvious?

13:00.800 --> 13:03.680
Xie Zheng and Fan Changyu's
little bastard.

13:05.360 --> 13:06.800
Little bastard?

13:12.200 --> 13:13.160
Bring her here.

13:27.440 --> 13:28.920
Where did you get her?

13:29.000 --> 13:30.960
Snatched her from Xigu Alley.

13:31.040 --> 13:33.240
She had a fine jade pendant on her.

13:33.760 --> 13:35.480
Looked like she'd fetch a decent ransom.

13:36.080 --> 13:37.720
So I kept her alive.

13:41.800 --> 13:43.720
She's worth far more than you realize.

13:45.200 --> 13:46.520
Let me go!

13:46.600 --> 13:47.960
-The girl stays with me.
-Let me go!

13:48.040 --> 13:49.080
You're a bad man!

13:49.160 --> 13:50.400
I'll avenge your brother.

13:50.920 --> 13:51.880
-Let me go!
-Swear it.

13:51.960 --> 13:54.040
Swear Marquis Wu'an
and Fan Changyu will die.

13:55.080 --> 13:57.720
Let me go!

14:00.640 --> 14:01.960
I swear.

14:02.040 --> 14:03.840
Let me go!

14:05.240 --> 14:06.920
You must die as well.

14:09.000 --> 14:10.440
YAMEN

14:10.520 --> 14:12.880
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

14:15.960 --> 14:17.000
Lord Li.

14:17.080 --> 14:19.280
Over 500 bodies
have been recovered in Lin'an.

14:19.360 --> 14:21.000
The injured are countless.

14:21.080 --> 14:22.320
Over a hundred homes destroyed.

14:22.400 --> 14:24.840
The townspeople lack food and clothing.

14:26.000 --> 14:28.000
Inform the Jizhou granary
and the Textile Bureau.

14:28.080 --> 14:29.760
Send emergency relief to Lin'an at once.

14:29.840 --> 14:31.640
House any displaced women and children

14:31.720 --> 14:33.040
at the Jizhou post station.

14:33.120 --> 14:34.080
Send word

14:34.600 --> 14:36.160
to neighboring counties to supply timber--

14:37.880 --> 14:41.160
My lord, please.
Your wounds are not yet healed.

14:42.720 --> 14:44.760
If I had not left Lin'an that day,

14:45.880 --> 14:47.560
perhaps this tragedy
wouldn't have happened.

14:50.840 --> 14:51.720
No one could have known.

14:54.280 --> 14:55.360
Please don't blame yourself.

14:56.680 --> 14:57.560
Report!

15:00.200 --> 15:02.200
Lord Li, Mrs. Fan has been located.

15:05.840 --> 15:07.320
Carry out my orders at once.

15:07.400 --> 15:08.400
-Yes.
-Send men with me.

15:08.480 --> 15:09.840
-Yes.
-My lord,

15:09.920 --> 15:10.880
you're not yet recovered.

15:10.960 --> 15:12.080
Let me go instead.

15:12.600 --> 15:15.200
I gave my teacher my word.
I will handle this myself.

15:15.280 --> 15:16.120
My lord!

15:54.720 --> 15:57.480
The Jizhou troops
have been sweeping this area.

15:57.560 --> 16:00.200
The men at the pass
can barely hold them off.

16:02.080 --> 16:05.200
But why can't we let
Li Huai'an's people find us?

16:05.920 --> 16:07.120
If you're that curious,

16:07.200 --> 16:08.720
go ask the master yourself.

16:10.800 --> 16:11.960
Fake soldiers…

16:12.760 --> 16:14.960
They must be in league
with Qingfeng Stronghold.

16:23.880 --> 16:25.040
Ma'am, what is it?

16:25.920 --> 16:29.720
I've brought
your young mistress's clothes.

16:29.800 --> 16:33.240
-Young mistress…
-She was drenched in sweat yesterday.

16:35.640 --> 16:36.480
Much obliged.

16:36.560 --> 16:37.600
You may go in.

17:07.240 --> 17:08.880
Good girl.

17:09.440 --> 17:12.119
The fever's finally broken.

17:29.120 --> 17:30.120
Granny…

17:31.120 --> 17:32.400
You're the one who saved me?

17:33.000 --> 17:34.640
Poor thing.

17:35.160 --> 17:38.640
First bandits, then a cold on top of it.

17:38.720 --> 17:40.800
You've endured enough for ten lifetimes.

17:41.360 --> 17:44.160
Good thing you have
such a devoted husband.

17:45.320 --> 17:46.480
They're all bad people.

17:46.560 --> 17:47.720
None of them is my husband.

17:47.800 --> 17:48.920
They're bad?

17:51.200 --> 17:52.160
Don't worry.

17:52.680 --> 17:54.360
I'll get you out of here.

17:55.640 --> 17:56.480
But…

17:57.600 --> 18:01.120
Girl, these old bones
can't move that fast anymore.

18:06.920 --> 18:09.640
Girl, where are you taking me?

18:09.720 --> 18:10.680
Girl…

18:17.200 --> 18:18.680
-The rear hills.
-Move.

18:33.200 --> 18:34.120
They're gone.

18:34.760 --> 18:35.680
Come with me.

19:09.920 --> 19:10.920
Come, Granny.

19:11.000 --> 19:11.960
Slowly.

19:13.200 --> 19:15.040
Why are there suddenly
so many troops here?

19:15.120 --> 19:16.520
This way.

19:18.240 --> 19:20.160
Granny, hide here.

19:20.240 --> 19:21.200
I'll go take a look.

19:21.280 --> 19:22.640
If they're men of the authorities,

19:22.720 --> 19:23.560
I'll come back for you.

19:23.640 --> 19:26.680
Be careful, girl.

19:27.200 --> 19:28.280
I will.

19:46.200 --> 19:48.040
Lord Li!

19:49.680 --> 19:51.480
Lord Li!

19:53.240 --> 19:54.800
Lord Li!

19:56.880 --> 19:57.960
Lord Li!

19:59.240 --> 20:00.600
Lord Li!

20:33.320 --> 20:34.960
Is capturing me worth risking your life?

20:35.040 --> 20:37.360
Is that little thing worth risking yours?

20:37.440 --> 20:39.400
-Is it that precious?
-That's none of your concern.

20:47.960 --> 20:49.120
Let go of me.

20:49.200 --> 20:50.720
Is it truly that important?

20:50.800 --> 20:52.160
Who gave it to you?

20:55.760 --> 20:56.880
A friend.

20:56.960 --> 20:59.400
A friend… What friend?

20:59.480 --> 21:01.400
Why do you care?

21:01.480 --> 21:03.440
What sort of friend is worth your life?

21:04.640 --> 21:05.800
You talk too much.

21:06.400 --> 21:07.400
Just do it. Kill me.

21:07.480 --> 21:08.480
Spare me the talk!

21:51.960 --> 21:54.840
Forget it. As long as you're safe.

22:01.680 --> 22:02.520
Whoa.

22:02.600 --> 22:03.440
Whoa.

22:07.000 --> 22:08.040
Finally.

22:08.120 --> 22:09.880
I heard your voice
at the foot of the mountain.

22:10.400 --> 22:11.240
Was someone after you?

22:13.720 --> 22:15.040
How did you get hurt like this?

22:15.880 --> 22:17.960
It's nothing. Just scrapes.

22:18.680 --> 22:19.920
There's a blind old woman.

22:20.000 --> 22:21.000
She escaped with me.

22:21.080 --> 22:22.200
She's hiding up the path,

22:22.280 --> 22:23.920
in the brush along the mountainside.

22:24.920 --> 22:27.720
Please send someone to settle her
somewhere safe.

22:28.240 --> 22:29.760
Tell her you're from the authorities.

22:29.840 --> 22:31.160
Don't frighten her.

22:31.240 --> 22:32.920
-Zhuo Ran.
-Yes.

22:33.000 --> 22:34.040
You four, with me.

22:34.120 --> 22:34.960
Yes.

22:37.800 --> 22:39.960
Are the townsfolk of Xigu Alley safe?

23:03.280 --> 23:04.280
Mr. Li.

23:08.480 --> 23:09.680
Mr. Li.

23:43.920 --> 23:45.080
Mrs. Yin.

23:49.040 --> 23:50.400
Mrs. Yin.

23:52.240 --> 23:53.640
Mrs. Yin.

24:31.920 --> 24:33.760
One, two, three.

24:33.840 --> 24:34.960
XIGU ALLEY

24:35.880 --> 24:37.160
Move!

24:40.240 --> 24:41.480
Who are you? Get back.

24:42.480 --> 24:43.320
Keep working.

24:43.400 --> 24:44.920
Lord Li ordered them burned quickly.

24:45.000 --> 24:46.000
We cannot risk an outbreak.

24:46.080 --> 24:47.400
Listen carefully.

24:47.920 --> 24:49.080
Lord Li.

24:49.160 --> 24:51.120
They were people. Show some care.

24:51.200 --> 24:52.320
Yes, Lord Li.

24:53.600 --> 24:54.800
Careful, all of you.

24:55.640 --> 24:56.680
-Yes!
-Yes!

25:21.160 --> 25:22.920
-Mrs. Zhao…
-Changyu!

25:47.360 --> 25:48.200
Careful.

26:18.760 --> 26:19.760
Where is Ning?

26:24.360 --> 26:25.240
Ning…

26:28.520 --> 26:30.240
She's missing.

26:41.200 --> 26:42.040
Changyu…

26:57.200 --> 26:58.400
We'll rest here.

26:58.920 --> 27:00.320
You, go find food.

27:00.840 --> 27:01.520
Right.

27:01.600 --> 27:02.360
-Right.
-Let's go.

27:02.440 --> 27:03.280
Over there.

27:10.000 --> 27:11.080
Enough!

27:17.800 --> 27:18.760
Cry again

27:19.280 --> 27:20.720
and I'll toss you in the river.

27:25.960 --> 27:26.800
Go.

27:27.360 --> 27:28.920
Fetch me clean water.

27:30.120 --> 27:30.960
Move!

27:46.800 --> 27:47.640
Little one.

27:48.840 --> 27:49.680
Little one.

27:53.240 --> 27:54.760
I knew you'd be frightened.

27:55.480 --> 27:56.880
Look how cute it is.

27:56.960 --> 27:57.960
Go on, touch it.

27:58.040 --> 27:58.880
Look into its eyes.

27:58.960 --> 28:00.000
You sick bastard.

28:01.520 --> 28:03.440
Are you shameless?

28:03.520 --> 28:04.880
Pick on Marquis Wu'an instead.

28:04.960 --> 28:07.240
What kind of man bullies a little girl?

28:10.040 --> 28:11.480
Why so serious?

28:12.080 --> 28:13.200
I was only teasing.

28:22.280 --> 28:23.640
She's having an asthma attack.

28:26.040 --> 28:28.400
Marquis Wu'an sired a sickly brat?

28:28.920 --> 28:30.680
-What a nuisance.
-Be quiet.

28:32.680 --> 28:33.840
There's no medicine.

28:34.960 --> 28:35.840
It's alright.

28:39.520 --> 28:41.160
I had asthma when I was young.

28:43.120 --> 28:45.160
Slow your breathing. It will pass.

28:48.640 --> 28:50.320
Didn't know you had that trick in you.

28:57.720 --> 28:58.560
Fine.

29:00.120 --> 29:01.880
The girl's under your care.

29:02.640 --> 29:04.280
Just don't let her die before we arrive.

29:09.200 --> 29:10.920
Thank you, miss.

29:16.880 --> 29:19.320
‎SUI

29:24.680 --> 29:25.720
Why?

29:27.360 --> 29:29.560
Why must you always defy my words?

29:35.480 --> 29:38.200
I meant to clothe you in silk,

29:38.280 --> 29:39.640
to deck you in gold and jade,

29:40.160 --> 29:42.240
to have you shine at my side.

29:42.760 --> 29:45.640
Yet none of these fine robes
can please you?

29:46.400 --> 29:47.600
Bring the tailor.

29:49.720 --> 29:50.960
Drag her out.

29:51.560 --> 29:52.880
Break her hands.

29:52.960 --> 29:54.560
-Yes!
-Mercy, Master!

29:55.080 --> 29:56.800
Mercy, Master!

30:00.680 --> 30:02.640
Such rare treasures.

30:02.720 --> 30:04.920
Such dazzling craftsmanship.

30:05.000 --> 30:06.280
And you feel nothing.

30:08.920 --> 30:11.360
Take the artisan. She clearly lacks taste.

30:11.440 --> 30:13.240
Take her out. Gouge out her eyes.

30:13.320 --> 30:15.000
-Yes!
-Mercy, Master!

30:15.600 --> 30:17.480
-Move.
-Mercy, Master!

30:19.520 --> 30:21.920
And the cook cannot prepare
a single dish you like?

30:22.000 --> 30:23.560
Then he has no use for his tongue.

30:23.640 --> 30:25.400
-Mercy, Master!
-Enough!

30:37.320 --> 30:38.800
You lunatic.

30:39.920 --> 30:41.600
Had I known this would be the outcome,

30:42.600 --> 30:44.440
I would never have saved you.

30:45.320 --> 30:46.920
You are mad!

30:49.320 --> 30:50.880
Mad?

30:51.960 --> 30:53.680
I give you everything.

30:54.520 --> 30:55.960
I am mad?

30:56.800 --> 30:58.880
Then why will you not bend to me

30:58.960 --> 31:00.440
and be mad with me?

31:02.880 --> 31:04.040
Every life taken outside

31:04.560 --> 31:06.240
was taken because of you.

31:07.280 --> 31:08.920
If you keep threatening the servants

31:09.560 --> 31:11.280
just to bend me to your will,

31:12.480 --> 31:14.440
more innocent people will die.

31:16.760 --> 31:18.960
Stop dragging others into this.

31:20.680 --> 31:22.160
If you truly want me to submit,

31:24.120 --> 31:25.280
then kill me.

31:29.720 --> 31:32.560
You know exactly
why you dare speak this way.

31:32.640 --> 31:36.480
You rely on the fact
that I still care for you.

31:38.920 --> 31:39.800
Very well.

31:41.880 --> 31:43.840
Bring the child.

31:51.120 --> 31:51.960
Mother!

31:57.320 --> 31:59.080
You may be unmoved

31:59.960 --> 32:01.400
by the lives of others,

32:02.160 --> 32:03.760
but look at him.

32:03.840 --> 32:05.480
So harmless. So trusting.

32:07.760 --> 32:11.640
Can you truly turn your back on him?

32:16.760 --> 32:18.800
If you mean to kill, then do it.

32:20.080 --> 32:21.680
He is your son.

32:22.760 --> 32:25.240
He never should have come into this world.

32:25.840 --> 32:27.160
Kill him first.

32:27.840 --> 32:29.360
Then kill me.

32:33.520 --> 32:34.920
My son…

32:37.280 --> 32:38.360
If

32:39.960 --> 32:42.440
I truly could bring myself to kill him,

32:43.000 --> 32:44.920
what would you do then?

32:50.920 --> 32:52.320
Do it.

32:53.520 --> 32:55.880
I will pretend I never bore him.

32:56.560 --> 32:58.200
I am done caring.

32:59.760 --> 33:01.000
Mother.

33:03.800 --> 33:04.920
You still

33:05.760 --> 33:07.480
do not understand.

33:08.720 --> 33:11.680
I am the one who most wants him dead.

33:14.160 --> 33:17.520
Do you truly believe I would not dare?

33:31.960 --> 33:32.880
No!

33:35.400 --> 33:36.240
You win.

33:37.320 --> 33:38.600
You win.

33:40.720 --> 33:41.880
You win.

33:43.160 --> 33:44.720
Please… Do not harm him.

33:56.800 --> 33:57.640
Well?

34:16.199 --> 34:17.080
Do you like it?

34:32.719 --> 34:33.719
Enough.

34:34.760 --> 34:35.800
Enough.

34:37.360 --> 34:38.199
Enough.

34:39.080 --> 34:40.120
Mother.

34:44.760 --> 34:48.440
At last. Our family of three,
together again.

34:54.080 --> 34:55.760
-Take him away.
-Yes.

34:57.280 --> 34:58.400
-Mother!
-Bao'er.

34:58.480 --> 34:59.920
Mother!

35:00.000 --> 35:01.520
Do not be afraid, Bao'er.

35:02.120 --> 35:03.400
Mother!

35:04.240 --> 35:07.480
Now I know where your weakness lies.

35:45.120 --> 35:46.000
Lord Li.

35:46.760 --> 35:48.320
What brings you here?

35:48.400 --> 35:50.600
Please, come inside.

35:50.680 --> 35:51.760
There is no need.

35:52.800 --> 35:54.800
We came to inform Mrs. Fan.

35:57.920 --> 36:00.800
Her grandfather and aunt…
Their remains have been found.

36:04.360 --> 36:05.960
They are gone as well.

36:13.440 --> 36:14.400
Lord Li,

36:15.160 --> 36:17.680
could you spare her this news for now?

36:18.320 --> 36:20.000
I fear she cannot endure any more.

36:21.240 --> 36:22.080
Very well.

36:22.920 --> 36:23.960
Where is she?

36:29.400 --> 36:31.840
Changyu appears unchanged on the surface.

36:31.920 --> 36:33.480
She eats, she drinks.

36:33.560 --> 36:35.040
But I know her.

36:35.120 --> 36:37.560
She swallows all her pain alone.

36:38.080 --> 36:40.280
Mrs. Fan possesses uncommon strength.

36:40.840 --> 36:42.680
Still composed after such devastation.

36:43.440 --> 36:46.040
No wonder she charged in and out
three times that day,

36:46.120 --> 36:47.760
saving so many neighbors.

36:47.840 --> 36:49.920
I only hope she does not break inside.

36:53.880 --> 36:54.880
Changyu.

36:59.280 --> 37:00.360
Changyu.

37:17.800 --> 37:21.120
THE LATE MOTHER MENG LIHUA
THE LATE FATHER FAN ERNIU

37:31.520 --> 37:33.000
KANG, THIRD DAUGHTER

37:38.640 --> 37:39.480
Changyu.

37:42.000 --> 37:42.840
Give that to me.

37:44.360 --> 37:46.120
The government will handle this.

37:46.200 --> 37:47.800
You do not need to do it yourself.

37:51.520 --> 37:52.720
The dead are gone.

37:53.600 --> 37:55.520
Do not destroy your own body with them.

37:59.560 --> 38:01.200
KANG, THIRD DAUGHTER

38:01.280 --> 38:03.160
Kang was alone.

38:04.800 --> 38:06.720
Two generations of men in her family

38:08.200 --> 38:09.680
fell on the battlefield.

38:10.800 --> 38:12.240
Her grandson Hu

38:14.000 --> 38:15.880
still wanders, searching for her.

38:16.960 --> 38:18.440
She had another grandson,

38:19.760 --> 38:21.320
taken for forced labor last year.

38:22.800 --> 38:24.400
No word of him since.

38:28.480 --> 38:29.360
YIN, NOODLE SHOP OWNER

38:29.440 --> 38:30.680
Mrs. Yin from the noodle stall.

38:31.880 --> 38:33.200
Her family lives in Anhua.

38:33.960 --> 38:35.200
We must send word

38:36.320 --> 38:37.680
to her family.

38:44.880 --> 38:46.080
Chef Li from Yixiang Restaurant.

38:46.160 --> 38:47.000
LI DEQIN, CHEF

38:48.120 --> 38:49.640
His father is 70,

38:50.240 --> 38:51.640
still working the fields.

38:53.080 --> 38:54.920
I do not know if he survived.

38:56.800 --> 38:58.520
I should go see him.

39:02.680 --> 39:04.040
Mr. Wang,

39:05.120 --> 39:06.960
who treated the yamen like his own home.

39:10.760 --> 39:12.880
And all the others.

39:17.120 --> 39:18.680
Until they are laid properly to rest,

39:19.880 --> 39:20.760
I will not know peace.

39:22.360 --> 39:23.520
Pushing yourself without rest.

39:23.600 --> 39:25.200
How much more can you take?

39:26.720 --> 39:28.600
Come, let's get you some rest.

39:28.680 --> 39:30.640
Resting feels wrong.

39:32.160 --> 39:34.040
The moment I close my eyes, I see them.

39:36.080 --> 39:37.440
All of them.

39:42.960 --> 39:44.760
And Ning.

39:48.720 --> 39:49.560
Changyu.

39:50.160 --> 39:52.960
Among the bodies recovered,
Ning was not found.

39:53.040 --> 39:55.080
She carries good fortune.

39:55.160 --> 39:56.960
She will be safe.

39:59.880 --> 40:00.760
Do not worry.

40:01.880 --> 40:03.760
I have sent more men to search.

40:04.760 --> 40:05.880
We will find her.

40:13.000 --> 40:14.800
I must find Ning.

40:17.440 --> 40:19.000
I must bring her home.

40:29.320 --> 40:30.520
Father. Mother.

40:30.600 --> 40:32.400
I'm going away for a while.

40:33.160 --> 40:34.560
If your spirits still watch over us,

40:35.600 --> 40:37.240
guide my path. Help me find Ning.

40:38.080 --> 40:39.120
Help me find Yan Zheng.

40:40.160 --> 40:42.280
Help me find every soul
from Lin'an who still lives…

40:42.360 --> 40:43.360
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

40:43.440 --> 40:46.000
…and bring them safely home.

40:48.040 --> 40:51.000
DIVORCE LETTER

43:23.920 --> 43:26.960
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

43:27.040 --> 43:27.920
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
